      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from ASME V&V 10 and Ansys verification manual were executed to confirm correct implementation of beam-column and contact formulations. Results matched analytical solutions within 0.5% for all benchmark cases. Code verification is considered adequate for the linear-elastic regime governing this COU."
