      "rationale": "Relevance of the quantities of interest was considered beyond the scope of the current credibility assessment phase. The QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) were inherited from the regulatory submission template and are assumed to be clinically relevant by convention. A formal assessment linking QoI selection to patient risk endpoints was deferred to a future activity and has not been completed at the time of this package generation."
