      "rationale": "Assessment of how closely the validation scenario maps to the actual clinical context of use was deferred as beyond scope for this phase. The validation activities replicate ASTM F1717 bench conditions, which are regulatory standard, but the degree to which these conditions represent in vivo spinal loading has not been formally evaluated. This gap was noted but not addressed, pending availability of clinical loading data from a separate study."
